ruct","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L432-L468"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">D</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v_1, u_1}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v_2, u_2}</a> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory\">MonoidalCategory</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightActionStruct\">CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightActionStruct</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max (max (max u_1 u_2) v_1) v_2)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A `MonoidalRightAction C D` is the data of:\n- For every object `c : C` and `d : D`, an object `c ⊙ᵣ d` of `D`.\n- For every morphism `f : (c : C) ⟶ c'` and every `d : D`, a morphism\n  `f ⊵ᵣ d : c ⊙ᵣ d ⟶ c' ⊙ᵣ d`.\n- For every morphism `f : (d : D) ⟶ d'` and every `c : C`, a morphism\n  `c ⊴ᵣ f : c ⊙ᵣ d ⟶ c ⊙ᵣ d'`.\n- For every pair of morphisms `f : (c : C) ⟶ c'` and\n  `f : (d : D) ⟶ d'`, a morphism `f ⊙ᵣₘ f' : c ⊙ᵣ d ⟶ c' ⊙ᵣ d'`.\n- A structure isomorphism `αᵣ c c' d : c ⊗ c' ⊙ᵣ d ≅ c ⊙ᵣ c' ⊙ᵣ d`.\n- A structure isomorphism `ρᵣ d : (𝟙_ C) ⊙ᵣ d ≅ d`.\nFurthermore, we require identities that turn `- ⊙ᵣ -` into a bifunctor,\nensure naturality of `αᵣ` and `ρᵣ`, and ensure compatibilities with\nthe associator and unitor isomorphisms in `C`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction","kind":"class","line":419,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L419-L468"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«termρᵣ[_]»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«termρᵣ[_]»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionUnitIso`, the structural isomorphism `- ⊙ᵣ 𝟙_ C  ≅ -`,\nallowing one to specify the acting category. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«termρᵣ[_]»","kind":"def","line":412,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«termρᵣ[_]»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L412-L414"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termρᵣ\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">termρᵣ</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionUnitIso`, the structural isomorphism `- ⊙ᵣ 𝟙_ C  ≅ -`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termρᵣ","kind":"def","line":410,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termρᵣ","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L410-L411"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termαᵣ\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">termαᵣ</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionAssocIso`, the structural isomorphism\n`- ⊙ᵣ (- ⊗ -) ≅ (- ⊙ᵣ -) ⊙ᵣ -`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termαᵣ","kind":"def","line":406,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.termαᵣ","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L406-L408"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊙ᵣₘ_»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«term_⊙ᵣₘ_»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TrailingParserDescr\">Lean.TrailingParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionHom`, the bifunctorial action of morphisms in `C` and\n`D` on `- ⊙ -`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊙ᵣₘ_»","kind":"def","line":402,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊙ᵣₘ_»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L402-L404"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊴ᵣ_»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«term_⊴ᵣ_»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TrailingParserDescr\">Lean.TrailingParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionHomRight`, the action of morphism in `D` on `C`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊴ᵣ_»","kind":"def","line":399,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊴ᵣ_»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L399-L400"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊵ᵣ_»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalRightAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«term_⊵ᵣ_»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.TrailingParserDescr\">Lean.TrailingParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionHomLeft`, the action of `D` on morphisms in `C`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊵ᵣ_»","kind":"def","line":396,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊵ᵣ_»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L396-L397"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalRightAction.«term_⊙ᵣ_»\"><span class=\"name\">