n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">inst✝²</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory\">MonoidalCategory</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction\">MonoidalLeftAction</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftActionStruct\">MonoidalLeftActionStruct</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.toMonoidalLeftActionStruct","kind":"def","line":120,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.toMonoidalLeftActionStruct","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L120-L157"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">class</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalLeftAction</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">C</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">D</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v_1, u_1}</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Category/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.Category\">Category.{v_2, u_2}</a> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Category.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory\">MonoidalCategory</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftActionStruct\">CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftActionStruct</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <span class=\"fn\">D</span></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (max (max (max u_1 u_2) v_1) v_2)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A `MonoidalLeftAction C D` is the data of:\n- For every object `c : C` and `d : D`, an object `c ⊙ₗ d` of `D`.\n- For every morphism `f : (c : C) ⟶ c'` and every `d : D`, a morphism\n  `f ⊵ₗ d : c ⊙ₗ d ⟶ c' ⊙ₗ d`.\n- For every morphism `f : (d : D) ⟶ d'` and every `c : C`, a morphism\n  `c ⊴ₗ f : c ⊙ₗ d ⟶ c ⊙ₗ d'`.\n- For every pair of morphisms `f : (c : C) ⟶ c'` and\n  `f : (d : D) ⟶ d'`, a morphism `f ⊙ₗ f' : c ⊙ₗ d ⟶ c' ⊙ₗ d'`.\n- A structure isomorphism `αₗ c c' d : c ⊗ c' ⊙ₗ d ≅ c ⊙ₗ c' ⊙ₗ d`.\n- A structure isomorphism `λₗ d : (𝟙_ C) ⊙ₗ d ≅ d`.\nFurthermore, we require identities that turn `- ⊙ₗ -` into a bifunctor,\nensure naturality of `αₗ` and `λₗ`, and ensure compatibilities with\nthe associator and unitor isomorphisms in `C`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction","kind":"class","line":107,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L107-L157"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.«termλₗ[_]»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalLeftAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«termλₗ[_]»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Notation for `actionUnitIso`, the structural isomorphism `𝟙_ C ⊙ₗ - ≅ -`,\nallowing one to specify the acting category. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.«termλₗ[_]»","kind":"def","line":100,"name":"CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.«termλₗ[_]»","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.lean#L100-L102"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/Monoidal/Action/Basic.html#CategoryTheory.MonoidalCategory.MonoidalLeftAction.«termλₗ»\"><span class=\"name\">CategoryTheory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalCategory</span>.<span class=\"name\">MonoidalLeftAction</span>.<span class=\"name\">«termλₗ»</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a hre